## Key Takeaways

**Technical problems require technical solutions first.**
No amount of content strategy can overcome a site that Google does not trust. Ed & Sy prioritized full remediation before any growth work, and that sequencing made the recovery both faster and more durable.

**Local SEO is a direct revenue driver for service businesses.**
For a home services company serving a defined geography, ranking for the right local keywords is the single highest-leverage marketing activity. Building out service and location pages with intent-matched content turned search visibility directly into booked jobs.

**A strong recovery builds the foundation for long-term growth.**
What started as an emergency fix became an ongoing growth partnership. When the foundation is right, each additional investment in SEO, content, or emerging channels like Voice AI compounds on a stable base.

